<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Kofta Curry Recipe</title>
	<link href="~/css/koftacurry.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>


    <div class="recipe-container">
        <h1>🧆 Kofta Curry</h1>
        

        <h2>Ingredients:</h2>
        <h3>For the Koftas:</h3>
        <ul class="ingredients-list">
            <li>2 cups Grated Paneer or Boiled Potatoes</li>
            <li>1/4 cup Cornflour</li>
            <li>1/2 tsp Garam Masala</li>
            <li>1/2 tsp Red Chili Powder</li>
            <li>Salt to taste</li>
            <li>Oil for deep frying</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>For the Curry:</h3>
        <ul class="ingredients-list">
            <li>2 tbsp Oil</li>
            <li>1 tsp Cumin Seeds</li>
            <li>2 Onions (Finely Chopped)</li>
            <li>2 Tomatoes (Pureed)</li>
            <li>1 tbsp Ginger-Garlic Paste</li>
            <li>1/2 tsp Turmeric Powder</li>
            <li>1 tsp Coriander Powder</li>
            <li>1 tsp Red Chili Powder</li>
            <li>1/2 tsp Garam Masala</li>
            <li>1/2 cup Cream</li>
            <li>Salt to taste</li>
            <li>2 tbsp Coriander Leaves (Chopped)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Instructions:</h2>
        <h3>Step 1: Prepare the Koftas</h3>
        <ol class="instructions-list">
            <li>Mix paneer, cornflour, garam masala, chili powder, and salt.</li>
            <li>Shape into small balls and deep fry until golden brown.</li>
            <li>Drain excess oil and set aside.</li>
        </ol>

        <h3>Step 2: Make the Curry</h3>
        <ol class="instructions-list">
            <li>Heat oil in a pan, add cumin seeds and let them crackle.</li>
            <li>Add onions and sauté until golden brown.</li>
            <li>Add ginger-garlic paste and cook until raw smell disappears.</li>
            <li>Add tomato puree, turmeric, coriander powder, chili powder, and salt.</li>
            <li>Cook for 5-7 minutes until oil separates.</li>
            <li>Add cream and mix well.</li>
        </ol>

        <h3>Step 3: Combine</h3>
        <ol class="instructions-list">
            <li>Add the fried koftas to the curry.</li>
            <li>Garnish with coriander leaves.</li>
            <li>Serve hot with naan or rice.</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
